default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAppraisals – e.g. regular appraisals carried out and career development discussed
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDiversity and unconscious bias training – e.g. training provided for all staff involved in recruitment and promotion decisions
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultTransparency of procedures and processes – e.g. individuals selected for posts or given more senior responsibilities through a fair and clear process
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultCommittee structures and balance of representation – e.g. women at least proportionally represented and not restricted to the least influential committees
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDepartmental openness and inclusivity – e.g. all staff invited to a weekly coffee morning, at which senior staff are accessible
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultDepartmental roles and responsibilities – e.g. less desirable tasks assigned fairly and transparently 
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultVisibility of women – e.g. care taken to ensure that the images around the university are not male-dominated, and a good balance amongst invited speakers
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultValuing staff contribution – e.g. achievements of men and women equally valued, and 
defaultteaching, research and pastoral 
defaultactivities all 
defaultrecognised 
defaultand rewarded
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWorkload allocation – e.g. all staff workloads modelled and analysed transparently to make sure individuals are not overburdened, such as with administration
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultInduction and training – e.g. all staff given a comprehensive induction and may be assigned a mentor, with the opportunity to express a preference about that person’s identity.
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultData collection (so the university/department knows what it must act on and can prioritise)
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultInduction, networking and mentoring (see the ECU report Mentoring: progressing women's careers in higher education
default)
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSkills development
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAppraisal and performance management
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultInclusion and communication (e.g. consulting staff systematically and utilising or setting up an early career researcher forum)
default=
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultParental leave.
default&#xa0;
